  "products": [
    {
      "id": "product-12",
      "title": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Sunway Lagoon Theme Park"
          }
        ]
      },
      "description": {
        "localized_texts": [
          {
            "language_code": "en",
            "text": "Experience never-ending fun at the award-winning water park in Malaysia — Sunway Lagoon! Explore six adventure zones within the park featuring thrilling rides and attractions. Come to the Amusement Park for cowboy rollercoaster action or view the world upside down at the 360-degree pirate ship. Get soaking wet at the Sunway Lagoon's Water Park, where you can surf giant waves at Surf Beach or slide down the vuvuzela, the world's highest and largest water ride. Set foot in Asia's first Nickelodeon-themed park, Nickelodeon Lost Lagoon, and go on splashy adventures with your favorite characters."
          }
        ]
      },
      "rating": {
        "average_value": 4.1,
        "rating_count": 35000
      },
      "product_features": [
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Multi-Park Extravaganza: Sunway Lagoon is a multi-park extravaganza, with 80 attractions spread over 360,000 square meters."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Exciting Rides: There are plenty of fun rides that cater to both children and adults."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Bungee Jumping: Sunway Lagoon offers thrilling facilities like the chance to go bungee jumping."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Kayaking and Archery: You can also learn archery or go kayaking at Sunway Lagoon."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_HIGHLIGHT",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Flying Fox: Experience the thrill of the Flying Fox at Sunway Lagoon."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "SUNWAY LAGOON AMUSEMENT PARK: You don’t have to be soaking wet to have fun. Head over to the Sunway Lagoon Amusement Park for a seriously great adventure. See a view like no other when you walk on Malaysia’s Longest Pedestrian Suspension Bridge, or see the world upside down when you spin 360 degrees on the Tomahawk and Pirate’s Revenge. Excitement is the name of the game here!"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "SUNWAY LAGOON WATER PARK: Beat the tropical heat in the Waters of Africa at Sunway Lagoon Water Park! Go for a spin in the loops of the African Pythons, or race your friends in an adrenalin-pumping ride head first down the Congo Challenge. You can also do the Cameroon Climb, get drop 15 metres then shoot back up 8 metres for prolonged fun. There’s something here for everyone, whether you are young or old, thrill seeker or beach bum."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "SUNWAY LAGOON WILDLIFE PARK: A Malaysia’s zoo where you get up close and personal with more than 150 species of animals from around the world at the Sunway Lagoon Wildlife Park. The fully interactive zoo attraction, from a journey of learning through our unique Wildlife Encounters , to getting entertained by our talented animal stars in the Wildlife Theatre and feeding our gentle animals in the Pet Village, there are various educational and interesting activities for the entire family!"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "SUNWAY LAGOON SCREAM PARK: Be afraid, be very afraid as you enter Lynton V Harris’ Scream Park, where great evil resides. You’ll be in for a spine-chilling and hair-raising experience at our live action scare extravaganza where fear is the name of the game. Be warned that this is not for the faint-hearted. Also, be prepared for a JAWSOME experience as we unveiled its latest attraction, Sharknado Alive."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "ASIA’S 1ST NICKELODEON THEMED LAND: Enter its majestic gates of Nickelodeon Lost Lagoon and be enthralled by this lost civilization surrounded by lush, natural rainforest.  Get ready for a wet and exciting adventure as you explore this fantasyland filled with colossal water rides and water playgrounds, canopy walks and meandering pathways, beautiful waterfalls and recreational camp sites. Set amidst 10 acres of lush tropical rainforest with more than 12 rides and attractions provides a mix of thrill and family friendly fun for fans and visitors of all ages. Behold, Asia’s 1st Nickelodeon Themed Land."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_INCLUSION",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "SUNWAY LAGOON X PARK: This is a shout out to all you adrenaline junkies, thrill seekers and extreme sports fans out there. Gear up for an aerial adventure on Malaysia’s longest Flying Fox and soar to great heights on incredible rides such as the Bungee Jump. Whether you conquer the circuit on a Go Kart or conquer the wild on an ATV, you are bound to get some heart-pumping action at the Sunway Lagoon X Park!"
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Restrictions: Please also kindly visit Sunway Lagoon Theme Park official website for height requirements for the rides."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Dresscode: Appropriate swimwear is encouraged at the park at all times for safety and hygiene purposes."
              }
            ]
          }
        },
        {
          "feature_type": "TEXT_FEATURE_MUST_KNOW",
          "value": {
            "localized_texts": [
              {
                "language_code": "en",
                "text": "Wheelchairs are available inside the park."
              }
            ]
          }
        }
      ],
